name: TSourceLib
short_description:
New version released in 2014-02-04.

TSourceLib reads and writes Tracksource-formatted maps as of 2013-04-18 specification.
The Tracksource Project produces detailed Brazil maps for GPS applications from editable source maps in GPS Trackmaker(r) (GTM) format combined with a complimentary GTI file which is a XML file containing information not supported by the GTM format such as street numbers and turn restrictions.
Tracksource Project website: http://www.tracksource.org.br

Library dependencies:

    GTMLib - GTM map format library from the same author and also hosted by SourceForge.
    PRTree - Khelekore's pr-tree library. http://www.khelekore.org/prtree
